winning_structure.name: UBX-AID-INI
winning_structure.description: Aiding position, time, frequency, clock drift

fields.name: ecefXOrLat
fields.description: WGS84 ECEF X coordinate or latitude, depending on flags below

fields.name: ecefYOrLon
fields.description: WGS84 ECEF Y coordinate or longitude, depending on flags below

fields.name: ecefZOrAlt
fields.description: WGS84 ECEF Z coordinate or altitude, depending on flags below

fields.name: posAcc
fields.description: Position accuracy (stddev)

fields.name: tmCfg
fields.description: Time mark configuration

bits.name: fEdge
bits.description: use falling edge (default rising)

bits.name: tm1
bits.description: time mark on extint 1 (default extint 0)

bits.name: f1
bits.description: frequency on extint 1 (default extint 0)

fields.name: wnoOrDate
fields.description: Actual week number or yearSince2000/Month (YYMM), depending on flags below

fields.name: towOrTime
fields.description: Actual time of week or DayOfMonth/Hour/Minute/Second (DDHHMMSS), depending on flags below

fields.name: towns
fields.description: Fractional part of time of week

fields.name: tAccMs
fields.description: Milliseconds part of time accuracy

fields.name: tAccNs
fields.description: Nanoseconds part of time accuracy

fields.name: clkDOrFreq
fields.description: Clock drift or frequency, depending on flags below

fields.name: clkDAccOrFreqAcc
fields.description: Accuracy of clock drift or frequency, depending on flags below

fields.name: flags
fields.description: Bitmask with the following flags

bits.name: pos
bits.description: Position is valid

bits.name: time
bits.description: Time is valid

bits.name: clockD
bits.description: Clock drift data contains valid clock drift, must not be set together with clockF

bits.name: tp
bits.description: Use time pulse

bits.name: clockF
bits.description: Clock drift data contains valid frequency, must not be set together with clockD

bits.name: lla
bits.description: Position is given in lat/long/alt (default is ECEF)

bits.name: altInv
bits.description: Altitude is not valid, if lla was set

bits.name: prevTm
bits.description: Use time mark received before AID-INI message (default uses mark received after message)

bits.name: utc
bits.description: Time is given as UTC date/time (default is GPS wno/tow)

structure.name: UBX-AID-INI
structure.description: Aiding position, time, frequency, clock drift

fields.name: ecefXOrLat
fields.description: WGS84 ECEF X coordinate or latitude, depending on flags below (value is degrees * 1e-7 when flag 'lla' is set)

fields.name: ecefYOrLon
fields.description: WGS84 ECEF Y coordinate or longitude, depending on flags below (value is degrees * 1e-7 when flag 'lla' is set)

fields.name: ecefZOrAlt
fields.description: WGS84 ECEF Z coordinate or altitude, depending on flags below

fields.name: posAcc
fields.description: Position accuracy (stddev)

fields.name: tmCfg
fields.description: Time mark configuration

fields.name: wnoOrDate
fields.description: Actual week number or yearSince2000/Month (YYMM), depending on flags below

fields.name: towOrTime
fields.description: Actual time of week or DayOfMonth/Hour/Minute/Second (DDHHMMSS), depending on flags below

fields.name: towNs
fields.description: Fractional part of time of week

fields.name: tAccMs
fields.description: Milliseconds part of time accuracy

fields.name: tAccNs
fields.description: Nanoseconds part of time accuracy

fields.name: clkDOrFreq
fields.description: Clock drift or frequency, depending on flags below (value is Hz * 1e-2 when flag 'clockF' is set)

fields.name: clkDAccOrFreqAcc
fields.description: Accuracy of clock drift or frequency, depending on flags below (value is ppb when flag 'clockF' is set)

fields.name: flags
fields.description: Bitmask with various configuration flags
